&lt;h1 id="no-truth-can-be-justified"&gt;No Truth Can Be Justified&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Oct 15 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;lsquo;Knowledge&amp;rsquo; is just our best guess at the time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;
Initial guesses at what &amp;lsquo;knowledge&amp;rsquo; was all about amounted to what is known as the &amp;ldquo;justified true belief&amp;rdquo; vision of knowledge, and it&amp;rsquo;s still the most prevalent idea today. Anyone who calls themself a &lt;strong&gt;Bayesian&lt;/strong&gt; is a justified true believer.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>